choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.
Breakfast: Greek yogurt with berries and honey, whole grain toast
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and balsamic vinaigrette dressing
Snack: Baby carrots with hummus
Dinner: Baked salmon with quinoa and steamed vegetables (broccoli, cauliflower)
